","tid":1491005,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4731764117dafc090e587b8572a03f68e16c637","tid":1491005,"uid":47905,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"係咪有必要組織一個私人檢控團隊<br />\n提供資金 法律援助 証據<br />\n去告黑警<br />\n<br />\n一般人好難有咁多資源"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:24:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會當助訟？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"「[助訟] 所針對的，是肆意和擅自介入他人的糾紛中，而被告人在當中並不涉及任何利益﹔其向某一方或另一方提供協助，並不存在任何適當理由或辯解。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然嚴禁助訟及包攬訴訟的規定，仍然是香港法律的一部分，但法庭對於該等規定已採取較靈活的手法處理而不予硬性施行，並會以更為敏銳的觸角來察看每宗個案的整體事實，以求當事各方的利益、司法公義的尋求、以及司法程序的持正之間能取得適當的平衡。<br />\n<br />\n可以預見，由第三方資助當事人進行訴訟的安排，在未來將會變得更加普遍。"},{"pid":"daabde18cded419ed6effc54d43d19f9788b5e5f","tid":1491005,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:53:53.000Z","msg":"推 有冇律師巴絲教路"},{"pid":"0e8c986a7f624d600d3d9fec219d1b43e044ad58","tid":1491005,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae638f49e989c5224536bea74cec786313e15b14","tid":1491005,"uid":53481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"麻煩改名叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民間律政司</span>"},{"pid":"21e01778d5fe4178a42b7282f53d48e6b259df51","tid":1491005,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae638f49e989c5224536bea74cec786313e15b14","tid":1491005,"uid":53481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"麻煩改名叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民間律政司</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"民間按察司啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02999eee4a454d0cdd40adbec86d523014ef8ac2","tid":1491005,"uid":69145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7c757f3ce22f9af4acbbec402d10