entOfJustice%2Fanswer15.shtml&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9qe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=a1a5fe3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/hkLegalSystem/theDepartmentOfJustice/answer15.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司司長亦有權介入任何涉及重大公眾利益的案件，如申請司法覆核以強制執行公法方面的權利。"},{"pid":"2d8c7ea88143145c8183e34b247d5cc1954e5ac5","tid":1491005,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"真係可以跳過？ 如果係既過 中央一定會釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69992088f35153aeb945aa6b5d995b4d4ce017f5","tid":1491005,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b84f892c21a5cb8c021afc33c7168db916e611f","tid":1491005,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"市民搵資料搵證據仲快黑警<br />\n律政司及黑警一眾搜證部門已成朝廷鷹犬<br />\n一係唔告，一係告條輕罪<br />\n事到如今，私人刑事檢控權係法律撚既最後一著<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在提起刑事檢控，所有人都認為須由政府主導。追源溯本，中世紀時，刑事法律是透過私人檢控來執行的。至17世紀，王室介入牽涉君主利益的案件，便開始了委任檢控官處理刑事案的做法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據普通法  市民有權提刑事檢控<br />\n惟市民提出私人刑事檢控的權利，沒有因而被政府取代。根據普通法，每名市民均享有與律政司長同等的權利提出刑事檢控。《裁判官條例》第14（1）條亦訂明，申訴人或告發人可按其意願，毋須事先獲得許可，親自或由其代表律師提出刑事檢控。<br />\n<br />\n私人刑事檢控不單是市民的個人權利，更是監察政府的重要和有力方法。在著名案例Gouriet v Union of Post Office Workers（[1978] AC 435, 477）中，時任上議院法官Lord Wilberforce就指出私人刑事檢控是「針對權力機關怠慢或偏袒的一項寶貴的憲法保障」（a valuable constitutional safeguard against inertia or partiality on the part of authority）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20190108/s00022/1546862377070/%E5%B0%B1ugl%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E9%83%AD%E6%A6%AE%E9%8F%97%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20190108%2Fs00022%2F1546862377070%2F%25E5%25B0%25B1ugl%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E9%2583%25AD%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E9%258F%2597%25EF%25BC%2589&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9qe24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=c8ce4aa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20190108%2Fs00022%2F1546862377070%2F%25E5%25B0%25B1ugl%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E9%2583%25AD%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E9%258F%2597%25EF%25BC%2589&h=27c0b788\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20190108/s00022/1546862377070/%E5%B0%B1ugl%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E9%83%AD%E6%A6%AE%E9%8F%97%EF%BC%89</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dHmAoS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dHmAoS</a>"},{"pid":"399f33a0c50fdf84131839d3ea59a68d2333e78e","tid":1491005,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78748e1cdf683d534c77e9ca5709b16fe3895bb6","tid":1491005,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ee4973ab0a3baabc28c73a1691ebb9605f3f5a7","tid":1491005,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29d28f3375f0b526de5ca1a0534f34a2bcb234b4","tid":1491005,"uid":270703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:33:08.000Z","msg":"律政司隨時可以take over個case然後放生"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:34:59.000Z","msg":"有得咁架?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:01:32.000